Class ChiSquareTestCategorical

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RemoveInsignificantAtributes

    public class ChiSquareTestCategorical
extends AbstractRemoveInsignificantAtributes
    This component removes "insignificant" categorical attributes by measuring if there are significant differences in values of a categorical attribute with respect to label attribute (class). As an input it takes Numerical attributes, label attribute and significance threshold as parameter for evaluation of attribute significance.
